BIC:

"Damn, ha ah aha ha," screamed Wildrider as he missed his opponent. He then
landed on the ground and was propelled forward by the blasts from Prowl, he
finally turned around and gunned it straight for Firearm.

Drag Strip barely dodges the missiles, even in his fast car mode, then as
the plasma burst comes by him he tilts himself, and drives by on his to
side wheels, towards Firearm, shooting twice from his cannon.
